parameters:
\N<Hakase-kun>Hmm... Is this bug the same as the
one I caught earlier?

\N<Boku>It's a huge spider web!... I can't touch
this... If only there was something like a wooden
branch...

\N<Boku>Ah! There's a discarded saw! It's rusty,
but it still seems usable... With this, I can fix
the bridge!
\N<Boku>Wow, there's a lot of junk here...
